- command template_fork: provide common_instruction and array of instruction, e.g. 
    {common_instruction: "Process a file", forks: ["a.c", "b.c"]}

- command @query workspace topic --- ask anythingllm 
- command @assistant fake assistant message
- command @tool-read fakes sending read command (after which true response is appended)
- Editor/patch: ensure header is a/ and b/ either through documentation or force

